cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper proposes a real-time expert system based on computer vision technology for anomaly detection of aerators using surveillance cameras. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses machine learning algorithms to build the feature classifier for anomaly detection. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper discusses the challenges of detecting abnormal conditions of aerators in intensive culture and proposes a solution using surveillance cameras. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses machine learning algorithms to build the feature classifier for anomaly detection. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the analysis of video data from surveillance cameras for anomaly detection of aerators.
